# Assets Insurance Contractual Regular Contributions Gross Amount

## identifier
de4629

## type
float

## definition
Report the total of all Contractual Regular Contributions as at the relevant date. These are the total gross premiums that are accepted through direct debit, have a specific contractual requirement for future on-going premiums, have an expectation of renewal each year (e.g. Yearly Renewable term products) or generally cause a policy to discontinue on cessation of future payment. It should be gross of all reinsurance.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Insurance.ContractualRegularContributionsGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
